{"tid":1009095,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國國務卿發表聲明祝賀農曆新年 vs  英國首相府迎春節貼春聯 慶祝中國新年","createTime":"2019-02-05T03:06:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-05T03:31:48.000Z","uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f669eb5419d0dd9d4c408d05aee92196d57bfcee","tid":1009095,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T03:06:20.000Z","msg":"美國國務卿發表聲明祝賀農曆新年<br />\n<br />\n2019年2月4日<br />\n<br />\n美國國務卿蓬佩奧2月4日發佈農曆新年賀詞，祝賀世界各地的朋友豬年快樂。<br />\n<br />\n聲明說：<br />\n<br />\n世界各地於2月5日慶祝農曆新年的朋友，請接受我最誠摯的祝福！<br />\n<br />\n在這個新的農曆年中，讓我們繼續加強我們和盟國與合作夥伴的關係，並邀請所有國家和我們一道努力，為子孫後代建設一個更加美好的世界。<br />\n<br />\n願豬年為所有人帶來健康、快樂和繁榮！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.voacantonese.com/amp/4771963.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.voacantonese.com%2Famp%2F4771963.html&d=Hj%2FeMeEVpmzVIwD%2FtvFBFtnRRycoFBIefads3zMUO1U%3D&h=796bc27b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.voacantonese.com/amp/4771963.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英國首相府迎春節 唐寧街10號貼春聯<br />\n 2019年 2月 03日<br />\n<br />\n在2月1日英國首相府的春節特別慶祝活動中，首相特蕾莎&middot;梅宴請了來自英國各地的約100名小學生。<br />\n<br />\n特蕾莎&middot;梅在講話中說：英國是英國華人的家，中國新年的慶祝活動讓我們有機會慶祝我們華人社區在英國生活中發揮的重要作用。<br />\n<br />\n「在慶祝農曆豬年來臨之際，也在英中兩國關係繼續向上發展之際，我向全世界各地慶祝中國新年的人們致以最美好的祝願！」<br />\n<br />\n雖然這是唐寧街10號第一次貼春聯，但這並不是英國首相特蕾莎&middot;梅第一次在首相府舉行新春慶祝活動。2017年農曆春節，特雷莎&middot;梅就曾舉行新春招待會，首相府內張燈結彩。她在致辭的最後，還用漢語祝福華人新年快樂。<br />\n<br />\nUK Prime Minister<br />\n@10DowningStreet<br />\nThis week the PM hosted a reception to celebrate Chinese New Year, the UK-China relationship and the British Chinese community<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/amp/world-47108789\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Famp%2Fworld-47108789&d=Hj%2FeMeEVpmzVIwD%2FtvFBFtnRRycoFBIefads3zMUO1U%3D&h=769b6ded\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/amp/world-47108789</a>"},{"pid":"9717d7a85367425364df9722ed66312936273d90","tid":1009095,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T03:08:24.000Z","msg":"農曆新年 vs 中國新年"},{"pid":"4bb3fc0dd51ede4e49e802754183c894a7ed3854","tid":1009095,"uid":6777,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T03:10:20.000Z","msg":"Chinese Pig<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nYear"},{"pid":"8d5599be03115f5ff396c3a7058edc0a6245ffe4","tid":1009095,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T03:11:10.000Z","msg":"奥巴馬有祝賀<br />\n侵侵無祝賀？"},{"pid":"dec0fbd1d36ed47d29490656cb3798b190581069","tid":1009095,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T03:19:25.000Z","msg":"UK Prime Minister<br />\n@10DowningStreet<br />\nThis week the PM hosted a reception to celebrate <span style=\"color: red;\">Chinese New Year</span>, the UK-China relationship and the British Chinese community<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔係 lunar new year"},{"pid":"edbca6b8f08d649596342f8a7658421e5ebe2cd1","tid":1009095,"uid":141782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T03:20:13.000Z","msg":"英國佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d5a9605b4dbcc07e024284a47b61bdf6188bc22","tid":1009095,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T03:27:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3046286e390c979f02fff9505931bd2f47451136","tid":1009095,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T03:31:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 英國"}]}